Original author: Matthew Breedlove (https://github.com/sirmalloc)  
Official repository: https://github.com/sirmalloc/ccstatusline

This fork is maintained for personal use and experimentation.

Fork notes:
- Exploring statusline customization for personal Neovim config
- May diverge from upstream in minor ways (colors, default segments)
- Adjusted default separator style from powerline arrows to simple pipes
- Disabled the file encoding segment by default (rarely useful in my workflow)
- Reduced default update interval for git branch segment (less frequent polling)
- Added truncation for long branch names (>30 chars) to keep statusline compact
- Disabled the file type segment by default (redundant with my existing config)
